04.09.wp.1644.77 /1 IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY NAGPUR BENCH, NAGPUR WRIT PETITION NO. 1644/1977 (Decided) (Abarao s/o Krishnarao Bonde vs.Parvatibai w/o Gendalal Shukla and others ) .......................................................................................................................... Office Notes, Office Memoranda of Coram, appearances, Court's orders Court's or Judge's order of directions and Registrar's orders ................................................................................................................................................................... CORAM : A.B.CHAUDHARI, J. DATED : 4th September, 2013. The Registrar (Judl.) of this Court to hear the counsel for the respondents and the available counsel for the petitioner and make a report as to whether it is necessary to continue with the present correspondence etc. as the matter is pretty old and the litigation must have come to an end. Let the report be placed before this Court on rd September, 2013

. JUDGE Sahare
